h=3cf3e363&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求右邊果幅地圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d72de710427f06d4a2d0ed0fbcf335f4129c383","tid":57894,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:32:06.000Z","msg":"去打真軍有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f2af6de8a8c06b27b6614cc345de857fc65bb82","tid":57894,"uid":3423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:51:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上次同師父行佢話何文田好猛鬼，好多靈界洞穴，又多積屍氣，真係被鬼迷都唔知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何文田山係開埠時嘅第一個公墓，即和合石"},{"pid":"f129dcfaac4632076b628d047696b9815ca2c865","tid":57894,"uid":6046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T14:10:55.000Z","msg":"前日撘過站行上月台真係嚇一嚇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/221052_4a8b35f3f0b635ad73d6de4f9fce6dec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F28%2F221052_4a8b35f3f0b635ad73d6de4f9fce6dec.jpg&h=28a70467&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f6d5b7fc6f851490a8b8cf7cb983bbd6909598bb","tid":57894,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T14:38:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c1a46b626299ff4a5abeba81bea01c7884f46752","tid":57894,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T14:50:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">何文田掘出亂葬崗</span><br />\n<br />\n何文田昨日發現「城市亂葬崗」。多名工人在水務署一個工地挖地時，意外挖出相信已逾半個世紀骸骨，致電報警，工人並充當考古學家，協助警方繼續挖掘，相信泥坑內最少有七副遺骸，部分是小童，法醫官到場檢驗及檢走骸骨化驗，亦會要求人類學桝授協助鑑定骸骨年期，及追查死者身份，工地需暫時停工。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/channels/news/20060411/20060411021911_0000.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fchannels%2Fnews%2F20060411%2F20060411021911_0000.html&d=%2Fj%2FDjIROJYT7MDUWTicArQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=2a37d62e\" target=\"_blank\">http://the-sun.on.cc/channels/news/20060411/20060411021911_0000.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23863c0ba007836872810ac50d1fca788d407151","tid":57894,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T14:50:59.000Z","msg":"專研墳場歷史的高添強稱，二、三十年代，何文田一帶是荒野，設有數個墳場，在二次大戰時是否為「亂葬崗」，則難以追查。戰後因城巿發展，墳場相繼遷往新界，不排除會「執漏冲一刋」。<br />\n<br />\n香港索償協會主席吳溢興表示，現今伊利沙伯醫院一帶，是戰時的著名「京士柏萬人塚」，埋葬逾萬名被日軍無辜殺害的平民。房屋及規劃地政局發言人稱，地政總署並無現場資料，應尋找本港的歷史檔案。"},{"pid":"4975f5cf86ae740de2a91cac4ea5fadbd63905f1","tid":57894,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:36:59.000Z","msg":"向住世界大酒店，即刻搭地鐵啦"},{"pid":"6d7f3d6a4ca9a344b1dcf83f90455a787800a6d1","tid":57894,"uid":51578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T15:43:42.000Z","msg":"上次行成十幾分鐘都未到月台<br />\n搵鬼去搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4539782149bdac362be84dad24335d45c3a8587a","tid":57894,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T17:06:12.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b69bbe93a6febb1ca19e0c41f2e819f6cd828159","tid":57894,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:46:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a719187fa56b85c03758004f2e1b9db4748049","tid":57894,"uid":60074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T06:47:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>轉自FB<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/28/192513_